{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Setting subgoals occupies a central part in AI's approach to complex problems or tasks (Russell, 2010).",
    "Particularly when the principal goal exhibits high complexity, AI can effectively comprehend and address the problem by decomposing it into smaller, manageable components.",
    "By dividing a complex task into simpler subtasks, AI can delineate a clearer path to achieving the overall goal.",
    "For instance, if an AI driving a car has a primary objective of arriving safely at a destination, it establishes subgoals like maintaining lanes, adjusting speed, and avoiding obstacles to achieve the primary objective.",
    "This method simplifies the complexity of the main goal, and through the successful accomplishment of each subgoal, the main goal is more efficiently achieved."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Setting subgoals occupies a central part in AI's approach to complex problems or tasks (Russell, 2010)."
  ]
}